EinPartikkel, a Pyprop package
==============================

This package contains modules for performing 3(2)-dimensional calculations with
one-particle systems. Time stepping, eigenstate finder and final state analysis 
functionality is provided.


Getting started
---------------

1) Create symlink to Pyprop location

	ln -s /path/to/pyprop pyprop
	
2) Compile all the EinPartikkel C++ libraries
	
	make
	
For examples of use of the EinPartikkel package, take a look in the example/ subfolder.
	
 
Package structure
-----------------
doc/                            Documentation
example/                        A few simple examples (in progress)
einpartikkel/                         
	__init__.py
	utils.py

	analysis/                    Stuff related to analysis of wavefunction

	core/                        Potentials and other core functionality

	eigenvalues/                 Finding eigenpairs
	
	propagation/                 Time propagation
		propagation.py               Control code for time propagation
		tasks.py                     Common propagation tasks
	
